/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

/build

# Sibling checkouts pulled in via `scripts/bootstrap-deps.sh`.
# The outer workspace's `[patch.crates-io]` block points at these paths; the
# checkouts themselves live in their own repos. Committing them here (as
# submodules or plain directories) would pin SHAs and fight the upstream
# PR flow, so we deliberately keep them out of version control.
/wolfram-expr-rs/
/wstp-rs/

# Local example paclets — developer scratch, not part of the published
# tree. The canonical end-to-end tests live under RustLink/Tests/.
/paclet-example/
*.paclet

# macOS
.DS_Store